  <header>
    <h4>Converters &amp; Filters</h4>
    <p>
      Prior to <b>MarkLogic Server</b> release <b>9.0-4</b>, converters/filters were bundled and automatically installed with MarkLogic Server. Starting at <b>MarkLogic Server</b> release <b>9.0-4</b>, converters/filters are offered as a separate package.
    </p>
    <p>
      This change affects the following XQuery API functions:
    </p> <ul>
    <li><a href="http://docs.marklogic.com/xdmp:word-convert">xdmp:word-convert</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://docs.marklogic.com/xdmp:excel-convert">xdmp:excel-convert</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://docs.marklogic.com/xdmp:powerpoint-convert">xdmp:powerpoint-convert</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://docs.marklogic.com/xdmp:pdf-convert">xdmp:pdf-convert</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://docs.marklogic.com/xdmp:document-filter">xdmp:document-filter</a></li>
  </ul>
    <p>
      Additional details regarding the <a href="https://docs.marklogic.com/guide/installation/intro#id_34694">MarkLogic Converters Installation Changes Starting at Release 9.0-4</a> are available in our <a href="https://docs.marklogic.com/guide/installation/intro#id_34694">Installation Guide</a>.
      <p>

      </p></p>
